{
  "title": "交换空间",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "交换空间是什么？ 略。<div><br></div><div><br></div><h1>查看交换空间的大小</h1><div><ul><li>交换空间是 /proc/meminfo的一部分：</li></ul><div><img src=\"quiver-image-url/2AC37F7504BC1D0519B2ADB63DA04B7D.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-15 at 6.38.06 PM.png\"><br></div></div><div><ul><li>交换空间也可以在系统的free报告中展现出来。</li></ul><div><img src=\"quiver-image-url/9C46C6F54D56EC9CE2720532C249520A.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-15 at 6.39.10 PM.png\"><br></div></div><div><br></div><h1>增加交换空间的大小</h1><div>Oracle数据库在安装时需要调整交换空间的大小，否则在安装时就会报错。</div><div><br></div><div><span style=\"line-height: 1.4;\">1. 建立用做磁盘交换空间的文件。</span></div><div><div><code><img src=\"quiver-image-url/9FC8FBAB630D421A6DBD85671EFA668D.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-15 at 6.51.39 PM.png\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.4;\"></code></div></div><div><br></div><div>2. 使用mkswap对该文件进行初始化。</div><div><span style=\"font-family: Menlo, Consolas, 'Ubuntu Mono', Monaco, source-code-pro, monospace; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.4; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0392157);\">mkswap ~/vmsp</span><br></div><div><br></div><div>3. 使用swapon命令添加该文件。（-v会给出一些对该文件的提示。）</div><div><span style=\"font-family: Menlo, Consolas, 'Ubuntu Mono', Monaco, source-code-pro, monospace; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.4; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0392157);\">sudo swapon -v ~/vmsp</span><br></div><div><br></div><div>系统重启之后就会失效。</div><div><br></div><div>在cent OS下安装swap文件</div><div><a href=\"https://www.centos.org/docs/5/html/5.2/Deployment_Guide/s2-swap-creating-file.html\">https://www.centos.org/docs/5/html/5.2/Deployment_Guide/s2-swap-creating-file.html</a><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div>"
    }
  ]
}